title: Preview: Neil Gaiman's Good Omens streams on Amazon Prime with stars Michael Sheen and David Tennant complete with all the beings to make a true Armageddon #GoodOmens #NeilGaiman #Video #AmazonPrimeVideo
body:
Preview: Neil Gaiman’s Good Omens streams on Amazon Prime with stars Michael Sheen and David Tennant complete with all the beings to make a true Armageddon #GoodOmens #NeilGaiman #Video #AmazonPrimeVideo

Who knew that when Neil Gaiman co-authored, Good Omens, in 1990 he would be back to bring the novel to life as the showrunner for this six-episode series about angels, demons and the end of the world in 2018.

All six episodes of Good Omens will be streaming on Amazon Prime on May 31, 2019

“Good Omens” is a tale of the bungling of Armageddon features an angel, a demon, an eleven-year-old…
